snippet.title: June 2017 Update for GOF ERAS2
snippet.description:
Latest version 2.6.0 with large update in DX9 64 bit. (DX8 and 32 bit versions still available) Features many new ships, characters, weapons, items and locations (to include new cabins and decks). Also sea shanties selected for all each nationality in the game and new sailing and on deck music. 

Mod team still working on more new colonies, quests, capabilities  and a possible version in DX11!

Game more stable than ever with new game engine (completely rebuilt) exclusive to this version. 

The only place you can get this awesome piratey adventure in a free download is Buccaneers Reef dot com
